Help Type: topic
Topic: command

Command Reference

Archive-first commands:
  create      Create an archive from source material at source stage.
  build       Build graph or summary stages from existing source data.
  estimate    Estimate words, token scale, calls, time, cost, and risk before build.
  status      Show archive readiness and object counts.
  index       Show the archive home/index page.
  list        List archive objects with filters, stable order, and cursor paging.
  find        Find objects by whitespace-separated keyword discovery.
  grep        Search objects for one exact continuous text phrase.
  page        Open one detailed object page by id.
  read        Print one object as continuous plain text.
  links       Show outgoing node links.
  backlinks   Show incoming node links.
  related     Show graph-adjacent knowledge units.
  path        Find a directed graph path between two nodes in one chapter.
  pack        Pack deterministic context around a known object id.
  export      Export a projection from the archive.

Command shapes:
  spinedigest create <archive.sdpub> [source] [--input-format <format>]
  spinedigest build <archive.sdpub> [--stage <source|graph|summary>] [--chapter <id>] [--confirm]
  spinedigest estimate <archive.sdpub> [--stage <source|graph|summary>] [--json]
  spinedigest status <archive.sdpub> [--json]
  spinedigest index <archive.sdpub> [--json]
  spinedigest list <archive.sdpub> [--id <ids>] [--chapter <ids>] [--type <types>] [--order <doc-asc|doc-desc>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json]
  spinedigest find <archive.sdpub> <query> [--match <any|all>] [--chapter <ids>] [--type <types>] [--order <doc-asc|doc-desc>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json]
  spinedigest grep <archive.sdpub> <query> [--chapter <ids>] [--type <types>] [--order <doc-asc|doc-desc>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json]
  spinedigest page <archive.sdpub> <id> [--json]
  spinedigest read <archive.sdpub> <id>
  spinedigest related <archive.sdpub> <node:id> [--json]
  spinedigest pack <archive.sdpub> <id> [--budget <chars>] [--json]
  spinedigest export <archive.sdpub> --output-format <format> [--output <path>]

Direct transform:
  spinedigest transform [--input <path>] [--output <path>] [--input-format <format>] [--output-format <format>] [--digest-dir <path>] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>] [--stage <planned|source|graph|summary>] [--verbose]

Maintenance:
  spinedigest meta <archive.sdpub> [metadata options] [--json]
  spinedigest cover <archive.sdpub>
  spinedigest chapter <action> <archive.sdpub> [options]
  spinedigest config status [--llm <json>]
  `chapter tree` without `apply` is read-only structure inspection; mutating chapter actions are maintenance.

